Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.52,0:00:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if the others are sleeping well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.06,0:00:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.95,0:01:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Getting Around at Kanyasai" The whole\Nschool's really going all out for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.66,0:01:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to be sure to hit\Nall the good places.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.71,0:01:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm, let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.96,0:01:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Quiz Club starts at 1:00...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.67,0:01:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A shogi tournament, huh?\NNot sure I'm up for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.26,0:01:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, the cooking contest\Nis worth checking out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.55,0:01:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm-hm. It's coming up tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.40,0:01:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kamiyama Prefectural High School\NWelcome to the\NKami High Homepage\NCulture Festival page here
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.66,0:01:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.91,0:01:45.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Days until Kanyasai: 1
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.13,0:02:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, may we have good fortune\Nfor the next three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.26,0:02:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May we be able to cross over this mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.36,0:02:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, it's culture festival time!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.04,0:02:39.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You hold your breath to make it through\Nthe bewildering day that confronts you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.88,0:02:46.06,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You know what this is, don't you?\NWhat do you want to do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.06,0:02:52.65,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The pain from shrugging\Nit all off as nothing{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.65,0:02:58.57,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}urges you on enough to be encouraging{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.57,0:03:05.20,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Catching hold but making a mess,\Nwe're still inadequate{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.20,0:03:13.13,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but as long as we can forge\Nour shining, unseen future selves...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.04,0:03:21.63,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Awaken and run where it takes you,\Nleaving mirages behind{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.63,0:03:28.22,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Run with your desire to change,\Nfrom your comfort zone into freedom{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.22,0:03:35.61,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Start choosing between now\Nand the brilliance you can attain{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.61,0:03:43.70,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Unaware of your destination,\Ndeep breaths following shallow ones{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.08,0:03:54.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Those Things Piled Up Endlessly
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.00,0:03:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.50,0:03:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.88,0:03:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're up early, Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.38,0:03:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got the culture festival, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.88,0:03:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.76,0:04:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you had some trouble, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.47,0:04:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.38,0:04:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.26,0:04:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, it's traditional that the\NClassic Lit Club's culture festival
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.39,0:04:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,can't ever end without there\Nbeing some trouble first.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.06,0:04:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody wants you leaving us\Nyour unwelcome traditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.56,0:04:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case, you could at least\Nleave me a good-luck charm, "Senpai."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.36,0:04:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.11,0:04:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There, you can have that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.82,0:04:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I supposed to thank you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.53,0:04:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, by the way, that's out\Nof ink, and the nib is split.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.58,0:04:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't dump your trash off on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.12,0:04:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.25,0:04:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.34,0:04:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I have time, I'll come down\Nand see how it's going, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.88,0:04:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.01,0:04:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the culture festival, Hotaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.68,0:04:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it would seem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.06,0:04:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Same old Hotaro as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.06,0:04:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to be enjoying yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.77,0:04:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, sure I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.06,0:04:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Kamiyama Culture Festival,\Nthe hall of fame of clubs!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.94,0:05:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, isn't that Mayaka there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.94,0:05:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's probably a Manga Club costume.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.70,0:05:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Judging by appearances,\NMayaka is on festival time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.37,0:05:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you thought up something, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.41,0:05:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heh, I {\i1}am {\i0}in the\NHandicrafts Club, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.83,0:05:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go bother her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.17,0:05:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mayaka. Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.76,0:05:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.88,0:05:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look good in those clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.39,0:05:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.18,0:05:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, who are you cosplaying as...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.14,0:05:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not use that word in front\Nof respectable folk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.15,0:05:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.94,0:05:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what {\i1}outfit {\i0}is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.69,0:05:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Frol.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.65,0:05:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Frol? Frolbericheri Frol?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.53,0:05:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm-hm. I've got gloves\Nthat I'll put on later, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.37,0:05:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.16,0:05:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's in your bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.45,0:05:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, a little something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.71,0:05:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds kind of shady.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.62,0:06:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayaka, are you with\Nthe Manga Club all day?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.38,0:06:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm-hm. I got stuck being a salesgirl.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.63,0:06:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And at a time like this, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.59,0:06:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, don't worry about it too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.22,0:06:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't help what's already happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.77,0:06:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.77,0:06:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now {\i1}this {\i0}is what I call a culture festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.86,0:06:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm-hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.32,0:06:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd heard about this, but it's\Nmore than I ever imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.70,0:06:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, what is this? It's pretty well-made.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.67,0:06:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.25,0:06:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.13,0:06:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Way too busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.50,0:06:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you done?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.80,0:06:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, all done.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.43,0:06:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.47,0:06:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Let's get this party started!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.52,0:07:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I have to step away for a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.44,0:07:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Handicrafts Club?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.69,0:07:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just for a moment. I'll\Nbe right up, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.83,0:07:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's quiet, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.12,0:07:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.54,0:07:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't dwell on it so much.\NIf you keep fretting like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.34,0:07:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,forget about Satoshi... even\NChitanda will get concerned.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.80,0:07:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.63,0:07:32.63,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Classic Lit Club Anthology\N{\i1}Hyouka{\i0} Vol. 46\NNow on sale
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.64,0:07:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, good morning, Oreki-{\i1}san{\i0}, Mayaka-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.10,0:07:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Chi-{\i1}chan{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.39,0:07:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost time, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.48,0:07:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.90,0:07:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's give it our all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.31,0:07:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.65,0:07:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is giving it our all\Ngoing to help this, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.03,0:07:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, there's no guarantee that\Nif we give our all, it will help,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.54,0:08:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but if we {\i1}don't {\i0}give our all,\NI can guarantee that it {\i1}won't {\i0}help!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.25,0:08:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indubitably.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.42,0:08:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I'm just going to buy them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.67,0:08:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Oh, that's not what\NI meant by saying that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.88,0:08:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, I {\i1}am {\i0}the one who placed the order.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.60,0:08:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many was the order originally for?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.85,0:08:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,30 of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.89,0:08:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many of them actually came?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.27,0:08:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,200 of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.90,0:08:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Galaxy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.99,0:08:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! My Saturn!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.08,0:08:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You finally showed up, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.74,0:08:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Fukube-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.25,0:08:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Been waiting long?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.16,0:08:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. We haven't started yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.13,0:08:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys, I'm really sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.93,0:09:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all my fault for not checking\Nmy email from the printers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.64,0:09:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody goofs up, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.39,0:09:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can say that, looking like {\i1}that{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.48,0:09:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to place\Nit all on yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.65,0:09:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're all friends, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.77,0:09:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can say that, looking like {\i1}that{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.61,0:09:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right. As club president,\NI should have checked it, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.20,0:09:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, after I turned in my draft,\NI'd washed my hands of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.28,0:09:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of the club members should\Nhave been responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.24,0:09:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! That's what I think!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.46,0:09:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm-hm... All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.71,0:09:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you've finally gotten\Nyour head on straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.84,0:09:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Again, you can say that, looking like {\i1}that{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.59,0:09:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, there's no more time\Nbefore the opening ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.93,0:09:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does anyone have any ideas\Nabout how we can sell
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.89,0:09:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the greatest number of copies?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.64,0:09:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How much for one of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.40,0:09:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,¥200.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.81,0:09:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's pretty cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.48,0:09:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The problem is the Classic Lit\NClub's lack of name value,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.82,0:09:54.07,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hyouka{\i0} Vol. 46\NNow on sale
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.94,0:09:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and our unfavorable location.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.57,0:09:56.95,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Elective Classroom ♪5
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.95,0:10:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. In other words,\Nboosting our name recognition
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.07,0:10:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and creating a better storefront\Nare most important.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.54,0:10:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Creating another storefront?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.70,0:10:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was only thinking about how\Nto bring customers way up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.83,0:10:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've turned my thinking\Nupside down, Oreki-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.38,0:10:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I wouldn't go so\Nfar as "upside down."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.71,0:10:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then again, can we get permission\Nto do so the same day it starts?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.93,0:10:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... What do you think,\NMr. Executive Committee Member?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.81,0:10:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm... It depends on whether or not\Nthey'd approve such a special privilege.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.98,0:10:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We could try asking the committee chairman
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.86,0:10:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or the student council president directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.03,0:10:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is the executive committee chairman?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.36,0:10:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could at least look\Nthrough the guide, Hotaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.91,0:10:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? Right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.20,0:10:44.70,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Committee Chairman: Tanabe Jiro
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.12,0:10:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First time I've seen it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.12,0:10:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, I wish you would have\Nnoticed the way this is set up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.26,0:10:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.88,0:11:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Anything stand out?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.14,0:11:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, the Classic Lit Club is at\Nthe end of all the club profiles, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.31,0:11:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked a huge favor and\Nhad them put us here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.81,0:11:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The executive committee\Ncompiled this, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.35,0:11:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.11,0:11:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an abuse of power.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.57,0:11:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, who cares? If you want to ask\Nthe chairman, try the council room.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.32,0:11:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to ask him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.36,0:11:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I suppose I could do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.49,0:11:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't have too much\Nluck with negotiating.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.87,0:11:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.83,0:11:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chitanda-{\i1}san{\i0}, what if you do the talking,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.17,0:11:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'll stand by you\Nto put in a good word?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.38,0:11:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, if you would!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.80,0:11:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well. Let's try it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.72,0:11:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't seem too eager about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.22,0:11:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, more importantly, I'd like\Nto devote myself to publicity!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.73,0:11:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that why you're dressed like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.56,0:11:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is just one part of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.56,0:11:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have something else up my sleeve.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.11,0:11:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a good idea in mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.28,0:12:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to drop the Classic Lit Club's\Nname as I participate
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.57,0:12:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,at the events and contests being held\Nduring the culture festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.83,0:12:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The plan is that by giving\Na strong performance,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.04,0:12:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Classic Lit Club's\Nreputation will increase.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.46,0:12:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just want to go out and have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.87,0:12:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is a good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.83,0:12:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.59,0:12:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.67,0:12:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to you, Fukube-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.25,0:12:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, hold on.\NYep, just leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.76,0:12:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good idea. I guess\Nthat's how we'll proceed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.47,0:12:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chitanda will negotiate us\Na better site to sell from,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.01,0:12:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and Satoshi will publicize us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.47,0:12:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go with that for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.14,0:12:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what about you, Oreki-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.73,0:12:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.86,0:12:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.82,0:12:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will mind the store.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.32,0:12:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right. I guess someone\Nhas to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.91,0:12:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.12,0:12:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we should get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.12,0:12:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The opening ceremony roll call\Nis starting soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.00,0:12:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.62,0:12:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.67,0:12:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would like to proceed with\Nthe assignments we just stated.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.42,0:13:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's try to sell as many copies\Nas we can! Our goal will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.01,0:13:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hyouka{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.55,0:13:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All 200 copies sold! Everyone ready...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.14,0:13:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.34,0:13:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.14,0:13:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.06,0:13:14.06,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shuubun{\i0} ('Middle of Autumn')\NWhen light\Nfindeth equal measure with darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.27,0:13:14.06,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Hyouka
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.06,0:13:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's centerpiece is obvious.\NHey, this looks like fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.44,0:13:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? The Quiz Club?\NHurry up and find your class.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.81,0:13:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, how about the Quiz Club's event?\NHey, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.32,0:13:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bunny rabbit?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.19,0:13:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is amazing, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.11,0:13:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.21,0:13:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hereby declare this,\Nthe 54th Annual Kanyasai...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.17,0:13:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to be open!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.06,0:14:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! He jumped over him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.27,0:14:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! He's spinning around!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.03,0:14:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I can't afford to stay here like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.25,0:14:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who wants to do calligraphy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.71,0:15:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calligraphy! Calligraphy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.13,0:15:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to try calligraphy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.05,0:15:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.55,0:15:10.59,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Chitanda Eru
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.09,0:15:13.68,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Chitanda Eru
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.09,0:15:13.68,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Cultivating rice is cultivating soil
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.68,0:15:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you like, you can keep it as a memento.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.85,0:15:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no... Oh, no...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.57,0:15:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The river from Tsukuhane..."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.99,0:15:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.95,0:15:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Spring has passed..."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.99,0:15:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!\NGot it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.25,0:15:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Though I part from thee..."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.16,0:15:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!\NGot it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.13,0:15:45.25,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Everywhere at once!!\NThe Hundred Poets Card Game Club
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.09,0:15:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.34,0:15:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One game?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.30,0:15:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.39,0:15:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"In the..."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.84,0:15:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.51,0:15:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please accept this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.52,0:16:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.44,0:16:08.57,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Executive Committee Office
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.07,0:16:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm finally here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.45,0:16:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.34,0:16:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pretty picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.01,0:16:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.52,0:16:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, did you need something?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.77,0:16:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I beg your pardon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.77,0:16:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I am here to see Executive\NCommittee Chairman Tanabe-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.48,0:16:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Tanabe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.99,0:16:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Oh, you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.03,0:16:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, please give the\NClassic Lit Club more selling space.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.58,0:17:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Global action! Global action!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.12,0:17:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me! Um, I am Chitanda Eru,\NClassic Lit Club president.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.75,0:17:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you see, I have a request to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.67,0:17:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please give the Classic Lit Club\Nmore selling space!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.09,0:17:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you ask me out of the blue\Nto give you more space,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.76,0:17:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't just offer something up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.68,0:17:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't? Thank you anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.52,0:17:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Wait, hold up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.48,0:17:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I meant, as a principle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.94,0:17:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have circumstances that\Nwould warrant it, tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.86,0:17:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mean it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.19,0:17:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.03,0:17:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that when I spoke to him,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.61,0:17:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukube-{\i1}san {\i0}was supposed\Nto be helping me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.37,0:17:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, when I hit the gas pedal, we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.58,0:17:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, whoa, whoa, no way, no way.\NYou're way too dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.25,0:17:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.25,0:17:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll cause an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.34,0:17:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.09,0:17:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That does sound like a problem. Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.13,0:17:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to help you out somehow,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.30,0:18:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the same goes for\Nall the other clubs, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.68,0:18:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't be partial to the Classic Lit Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.97,0:18:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then there isn't anything you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.56,0:18:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.90,0:18:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, however, if you get the other clubs
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.36,0:18:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to let you leave some of the Classic Lit\NClub's anthologies at their spots,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.94,0:18:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd have no problem with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.91,0:18:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is a great way to do it!\NI will consider it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.53,0:18:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.55,0:18:39.80,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to the Manga Club\NCollections now on sale!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.19,0:18:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.81,0:18:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.48,0:18:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Ibara, you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.61,0:18:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kochi-{\i1}senpai{\i0}, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.66,0:19:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You even have a katana for yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.08,0:19:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It's just a fake plastic one, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.80,0:19:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should have come up with\Nsomething for your feet, too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.84,0:19:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that, she decided\Nto cosplay after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.51,0:19:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And after objecting as\Nhard as she did, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.76,0:19:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She should have just done\Nas Kochi said from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.18,0:19:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, there's no call for that kind of talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.15,0:19:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.15,0:19:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Yuasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.86,0:19:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, President.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.94,0:19:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.57,0:19:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did that cost a lot?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.57,0:19:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just the price of the belt.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.20,0:19:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. If you have the receipt, I'll take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.37,0:19:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's all right.\NNevermind that, President, can I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.67,0:19:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.79,0:19:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, nevermind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.55,0:19:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.42,0:20:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.51,0:20:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.22,0:20:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It really is hard to ask if I can\Nput copies of {\i1}Hyouka{\i0} in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.39,0:20:12.77,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Zeami's
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.35,0:20:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.81,0:20:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What outfit is this you're wearing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.61,0:20:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This? It's Frol. Ever heard of\N{\i1}They Were Eleven{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.44,0:20:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.65,0:20:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never heard of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.78,0:20:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was an old science fiction manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.28,0:20:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I consider it a masterpiece.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.91,0:20:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me borrow it sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.29,0:20:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm-hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.00,0:20:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What? What are you borrowing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.92,0:20:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.08,0:20:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, everyone,\Nlet's all get fired up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.42,0:20:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.84,0:20:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, are you open yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.80,0:20:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come right on in!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.43,0:20:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have our first customers!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.97,0:20:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on in!\NWelcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.52,0:20:54.27,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Classic Lit Club Anthology\N{\i1}Hyouka{\i0} Vol. 46\NNow on sale
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.28,0:21:03.65,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Goal: Sell out all 200 copies!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.36,0:21:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.12,0:21:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three cheers for store-minding.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.46,0:21:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'll mark down the ones\Nwe're definitely going to sell.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.79,0:21:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And given the circumstances,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.38,0:21:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,let's assume the four Classic Lit Club\Nmembers will each buy two.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.17,0:21:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Add to that our advisor and the archives,\Nand that's 12 gone, for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.14,0:21:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, even at just that,\NI'd say we did well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.69,0:21:39.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,A Capella Club
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.80,0:22:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Anyone seen my apple juice?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.38,0:22:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.39,0:22:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, I didn't even have any of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.76,0:22:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that piece of paper there?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.35,0:22:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.74,0:22:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-oh, getting sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.28,0:22:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.33,0:22:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, a punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.37,0:22:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he a punk?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.50,0:22:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.33,0:22:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing... er, I mean,\Nwe're selling anthologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.17,0:22:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean, all of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.76,0:22:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Long story.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.80,0:22:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, one, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.26,0:22:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, he's a customer? Is he a customer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.98,0:22:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to be gracious...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.27,0:23:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That will be ¥200.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.86,0:23:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, I can't even manage to smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.86,0:23:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.32,0:23:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.82,0:23:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.99,0:23:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This! Would you mind\Nif I had a look at it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.20,0:23:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean this?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.54,0:23:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm-hm. This is it! This is perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.79,0:23:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.67,0:23:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.29,0:23:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in the Clothing Club, you see.\NWe're having a fashion show,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.26,0:23:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I forgot something to go in\Nmy formalwear breast pocket!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.97,0:23:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This would be just the thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.93,0:23:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.76,0:23:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Really?! You'd really give it to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.39,0:23:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was going to throw it\Naway anyhow. Help yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.48,0:23:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well then, take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.23,0:23:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a priority pass to our show,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.94,0:23:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so if you bring that to\Nthe Clothing Club room,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.07,0:23:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they'll set you up with\Na top-notch ensemble.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.36,0:23:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.24,0:23:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satoshi's about the only one who might go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.91,0:23:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, I guess he has his own style,\Nhuh? Well, don't need that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.87,0:24:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although, that is one issue sold.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.31,0:24:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! I did it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.44,0:24:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say there!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.73,0:24:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.98,0:24:28.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a commemorative picture taken!\NPhotography Club
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.49,0:24:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How would you like to take a photo?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.49,0:24:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.17,0:24:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! Oh, no! Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.80,0:24:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time something catches\Nmy interest, I come to a halt,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.42,0:24:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which is keeping me from\Naccomplishing my duty!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.47,0:24:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Occult Club! Occult Club!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.05,0:24:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to summon a UFO with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.81,0:25:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We also have an exhibit\Nof spirit photography.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.10,0:25:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now displaying the {\i1}Enterprise{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.56,0:25:03.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Industrial Arts Club
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.10,0:25:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although we're\Nabout to hold the launching ceremony!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.11,0:25:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come witness three months\Nof work go down the tubes!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.53,0:25:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Global Action exhibit here!\NMagic charm, anybody?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.61,0:25:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The A Capella Club is\Nsinging in the courtyard!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.24,0:25:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to the Shogi Club tournament!\NSee the Debate Club arguing!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.99,0:25:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Occult Club! Occult Club here! The History\NClub has recreated Kamiyama Castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.04,0:25:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are there a pair of glasses anywhere
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.13,0:25:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that only let you see straight ahead?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.23,0:25:53.28,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This situation is an unscientific\Nmontage of emotions{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.90,0:25:56.57,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who is calling whom?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.57,0:26:02.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your gaze darts away when I turn around\N(I can feel it){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.54,0:26:04.79,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's unkind to tell me I'm imagining things{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.79,0:26:10.34,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They say having antennas\Nis a talent, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.34,0:26:15.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I mean I want to know\N(I mean) (don't you?){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.38,0:26:22.18,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll turn up the heat on your youth\Nfor you now, while there's time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.18,0:26:26.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If we can solve this tomorrow,\Nwhy not solve it right now?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.85,0:26:32.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to solve your mystery{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.44,0:26:37.15,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Track down that secretive boyish figure!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.15,0:26:44.70,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}(Today) you are a fantasy,\Ndrawing me to you, no fair!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.70,0:26:50.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My curiosity is expanding,\Nlack of tricks notwithstanding{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.38,0:26:57.30,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm fascinated, and I have to know, why?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.81,0:27:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, "A Corpse By Evening."
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.52,0:27:13.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,A Corpse By Evening
